'''Mafuro''' (''pasture or grazing land'' in English) inzvimbo dzine huswa yokuti mhuka dzekupfuyiwa dzinoenda dzichinodya kana kuti kufura huswa. Kuma[[ruwa]] mafuro inzvimbo dzakatambanuka dzisina  minda yakasimwa mumera; vafudzi vanoendako nenmombe vachidzifudza kunova kudzichengeta uye kudzvirira kuti dzisaende kune minda. Kumapurazi makuru, mafuro anenge akakomberedza newaya zvokuti vafudzi hava basa guru rokuti vateveredze mombe - chavo kudzichengeta kubva kumbavha.

